{"tid":1682134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Twitter：無意進軍中國市場，以確保用戶可以參與對話並在此過程中感到安全","createTime":"2019-10-30T01:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T02:36:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2b56792453c9fde015538cc639a67c7cadb98b","tid":1682134,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2485264/20191029_16_v2_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2485264%2F20191029_16_v2_600.png&h=e6a8ff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國社交平台Twitter（美︰TWTR）早前公布的業務遜預期，外界關注目前在中國被屏蔽的Twitter會否試圖開拓中國市場，尋找新機遇，惟Twitter財務總監西格爾（Ned Segal）表明，無計劃進入中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n西格爾接受CNBC訪問時表示，Twitter無意進入中國市場，強調希望用戶相信他們所看到的資訊，加入討論並覺得安全。<br />\n<br />\n西格爾稱目前的發展方向，是致力提升現有1.45億可獲利每日活躍用戶的使用體驗。<br />\n<br />\n廣告是Twitter重要收入來源，西格爾指Twitter正努力改變廣告形式，加強與用戶的相關性，讓廣告客戶的影片更能與用戶連結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2485264/Twitter稱無意進軍中國%20希望用戶相信所看資訊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2485264%2FTwitter%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2520%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%89%80%E7%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt33ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=83bde54b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2485264/Twitter稱無意進軍中國%20希望用戶相信所看資訊</a>"},{"pid":"ede05ea79db54d62b1f643e4b8afd9e9cb6616fd","tid":1682134,"uid":89868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45dc0aa4b05b9e7fc72a77e5155c4e9260cc6ef","tid":1682134,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087e03c5827c029bf7fff90f9e90b70df8827d16","tid":1682134,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"牙...牙推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ac53d48c5585e451a6ef9e94d091c28ce4b907","tid":1682134,"uid":65686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T01:17:13.000Z","msg":"係得豬西伯格先做呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491866a352d7e4cd5bddaf20d318607210939ccd","tid":1682134,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"[11.9集會活動第二擊] 你有想過香港有一幅屬於自己的兄弟之吻嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1682179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1682179</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}